<div class="content">
	<p>The <a href="#apps/connection-manager">Connection Manager</a> app allows you to easily view additional details about your connections alongside their names and icons.</p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-tags"></i>The View Details Menu</h2>
			<p>The View menu provides the ability to select among various file details to show. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="nested dropdown menu" src="images/help/building-social-network/viewing-connection-details/view-details-menu@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">"Details" on the View Menu</div>
			</div>

			<p>The connection details that you can display include:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><label>Location</label></li>
				<li><label>Occupation</label></li>
				<li><label>Age</label></li>
				<li><label>Gender</label></li>
				<li><label>Date</label>
					<ul>
						<li><label>Birth Date</label></li>
						<li><label>Join Date</label></li>
						<li><label>Connect Date</label></li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Connection Details</h2>
			<p>Connection details are displayed in grey rounded boxes underneath the connection's name.</p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/building-social-network/viewing-connection-details/view-connections-location.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="View Location (Cards)"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/building-social-network/viewing-connection-details/view-connections-location.png" /></a>
